data.title: Handbook of Geological Terms and Geology
data.meta_description: Handbook of Geological Terms and Geology - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document appears to be the contents page and introduction for a geological handbook from 1859. It lists the various orders and families of minerals that were known at the time, arranged by Professor Weiss of Berlin. The most abundant minerals within each family are italicized. The introduction discusses the need for concise explanations of geological terms and technicalities to make the science more accessible to general readers and students.
